properties.name: MOD: Mind Over Distraction
properties.description: The game aims to enhance cognitive abilities and overall functioning through affordable and efficient digital assistance. The project design focuses on creating four modules: Memory, Attention, Focus, and Emotional Regulation, each targeting specific cognitive domains.
